These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, january, july
City: venice, san-francisco, berlin
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, traveling, writing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, mystery
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, malaysian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, country, indie
 1. the person watching documentary movies is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6
 2. the australian is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 3. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 4. the malaysian is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the fan of indie##7
 5. the fan of indie is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is the fan of reggae##1
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is not the british##6
 8. the australian is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the fan of indie is not the person who's hobby is writing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |
| Birthday      | november       | january  | july     |
| City          | berlin       | san-francisco  | venice    |
| Hobby         | card-games  | writing   | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | drama     |
| Nationality   | australian  | malaysian | british   |
| Music-Genre           | country  | reggae      | indie  |

