.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-2::.
There 3 different types of food: orange, papaya, plum
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, hiking
3 different pets are kept: goat, frog, bird
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, april, july
House: victorian, tower, cape-cod
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
 2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the person eating plum##7
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
 6. the person eating papaya is between the victorian house and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person eating plum and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
 9. the tower house is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the goat is not the victorian house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2        |      3       |
| Food          | orange       | papaya         | plum         |
| Hobby         | board-games  | hiking         | card-games   |
| Pet           | goat     | bird | frog |
| Birthday   | april         | july         | august        |
| House   | tower      | cape-cod        | victorian   |
| Sport         | snowboarding | volleyball     | soccer       |

