3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, dunhill, swisher
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, german, japanese
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, trike
 1. the person driving the car is the japanese##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person who's sport is tennis##7
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 8. the person driving the trike is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the german##5
10. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the german##5
11. the montecristo-smoker is not the person traveling to hamburg##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3      |
| Sport      | tennis    | snowboarding    | ice-hockey |
| Hobby         | fishing  | video-games | puzzles     |
| City   | paris  | hamburg | san-francisco         |
| Cigar   | swisher     | dunhill      | montecristo     |
| Nationality   | japanese | german      | canadian    |
| Transport     | car      | trike       | quad-bike   |

