6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
7. the montecristo-smoker is the person who's birthday is in october##1
8. the person playing poker is somewhere between the person eating carrot and the person drinking lemonade##7
9. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person eating carrot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | cola       | iced-tea      | lemonade    |
| Food          | carrot     | papaya        | kiwi        |
| Birthday           | august  | october | may   |
| Game   | whist | poker           | bridge |
| Cigar   | game  | montecristo    | pall-mall   |
| Transport     | van        | taxi          | car         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-18::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, snowboarding, cricket
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, ship, skateboard
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, manager, musician
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, fantasy, horror
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, r&b, reggae
3 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, chess
 1. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
 2. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person driving the trike is the fan of r&b##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the person watching adventure movies##7
 5. the journalist is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 6. the manager is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
 7. the journalist is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the fan of reggae##2
 8. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the musician##5
 9. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the trike is not the manager##6
11. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the journalist##1
12. the journalist is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3

