.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, nurse, paramedic
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, romance, satire
City: liverpool, new-york, london
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip, sunflower
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, swimming, volleyball
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, cain, chaman
 1. the accountant is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
 2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 3. the person who growsrose is somewhere between the person who growstulip and the person who growssunflower##7
 4. the paramedic is the person watching satire movies##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person watching satire movies##1
 6. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the accountant##1
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is the chaman-smoker##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5
10. the person who growsrose is the person watching romance movies##1
11. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person who growssunflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Job           | paramedic    | accountant | nurse    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire       | romance    | action   |
| City   | london        | new-york  | liverpool |
| Flower           | sunflower       | rose   | tulip     |
| Sport         | snowboarding | volleyball | swimming |
| Cigar     | cain       | bluemaster | chaman    |

 